From 5946387114ad910f284a67f35ca0378c895de8d8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:05:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Repair malformed TypeScript introduced by RepoDiet PR #14

Restore src/lib/feed-curation.ts and src/lib/token-quote.ts from commit
824075afe776067bf00343581105d6a1f5e61178 (pre-RepoDiet PR #14).

Broken commit: a39937b4b05691a7cc57f2824f18745dd61bea3f merged PR #14 which
left incomplete constant declarations and dangling type properties in:
- src/lib/feed-curation.ts (unfinished BLUE_CHIP_NAME_HINTS, removed BLUE_CHIP_SYMBOLS)
- src/lib/token-quote.ts (dangling type properties, missing isTokenQuoteReliable header)

No unrelated changes. RepoDiet artifacts under repodiet/ are not reverted.
---
 src/lib/feed-curation.ts | 39 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/lib/token-quote.ts   |  3 +++
 2 files changed, 42 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/lib/feed-curation.ts b/src/lib/feed-curation.ts
index e84761c..b0953e7 100644
--- a/src/lib/feed-curation.ts
+++ b/src/lib/feed-curation.ts
@@ -4,7 +4,46 @@
 
